1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,620 --> 00:00:55,540
=Episode 11=

3
00:01:07,359 --> 00:01:07,920
Liuli.

4
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:10,560
Why did you react so fiercely

5
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:12,120
when you saw the Queen of Xiling?

6
00:01:13,239 --> 00:01:13,840
You seemed

7
00:01:14,799 --> 00:01:16,040
to hate her even more than I do.

8
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:18,560
I've always been stubborn
since childhood.

9
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:22,920
Your Majesty is the one
I've chosen in my heart.

10
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:24,599
What you love,

11
00:01:25,239 --> 00:01:26,799
I will cherish even more.

12
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,079
What you despise,

13
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:31,640
I will hate with all my being.

14
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:34,319
As long as you never abandon me,

15
00:01:34,959 --> 00:01:37,200
I will follow you
to the end of the world.

16
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:42,200
How can I trust you?

17
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:45,079
I don't need your trust.

18
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,599
I won't say "thank you",

19
00:01:48,079 --> 00:01:51,840
because it means nothing in this world.

20
00:01:52,799 --> 00:01:54,439
I will prove through my actions

21
00:01:54,799 --> 00:01:55,680
that in this world,

22
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:59,079
love will be rewarded.

23
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:00,840
But do you know

24
00:02:01,359 --> 00:02:02,480
what I hate the most

25
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,120
is not ingratitude,

26
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:06,200
but abandonment

27
00:02:06,719 --> 00:02:07,680
and betrayal?

28
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:12,199
I was confined to the music house,

29
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:15,319
and I could only see
a corner of the street.

30
00:02:16,039 --> 00:02:17,759
Whenever I leaned against the railing,

31
00:02:18,919 --> 00:02:21,479
I could only try my best
to please passersby.

32
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,919
I seemed to be part of the scenery,

33
00:02:25,159 --> 00:02:26,400
but being inside the scenery

34
00:02:27,759 --> 00:02:29,120
felt like standing
at the edge of an abyss.

35
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,960
Now, thanks to Your Majesty,

36
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,800
I've been fortunate enough
to escape that confinement

37
00:02:34,479 --> 00:02:36,439
and catch a glimpse
of pavilions and towers

38
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,159
and the beautiful world.

39
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:42,960
I used to pity myself,

40
00:02:43,599 --> 00:02:46,199
thinking I alone was lower
than the dust.

41
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,319
Only today did I learn

42
00:02:50,159 --> 00:02:52,759
that Your Majesty shares a past
just like mine

43
00:02:54,319 --> 00:02:55,479
and the same pain.

44
00:02:57,520 --> 00:03:01,400
I feel all the closer
to Your Majesty now.

45
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,759
Even the pain of your past,

46
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:06,599
I can feel it as if it were my own.

47
00:03:07,319 --> 00:03:08,599
It wrenches my heart.

48
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,039
In this way,

49
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,479
I crossed the line

50
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,800
and incurred your suspicion.

51
00:03:18,319 --> 00:03:20,439
I was too eager.

52
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,360
Liuli.

53
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:25,319
I've seen the look
in your eyes tonight before,

54
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,680
and only in two kinds of people.

55
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:28,800
One,

56
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:30,879
those who are ready to die.

57
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:32,879
The other,

58
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,919
those who have someone they'd die for.

59
00:03:39,080 --> 00:03:39,800
So,

60
00:03:40,719 --> 00:03:41,639
I choose to trust you.

61
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:45,199
Does it still hurt?

62
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:48,800
Thanks for your precious herb,

63
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,599
my long-standing illness was cured.

64
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:53,680
I've long since recovered.

65
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,560
But what is the pain of the flesh

66
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,520
compared to

67
00:03:57,840 --> 00:04:01,520
the agony of being betrayed
by the one you trust?

68
00:04:05,759 --> 00:04:06,840
I only hope Your Majesty

69
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,599
no longer doubts my sincerity.

70
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:11,960
I understand your sincerity now.

71
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,400
I will not let you down.

72
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:25,120
We're truly a perfect match.

73
00:04:25,399 --> 00:04:27,240
My martial skills have improved lately,

74
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,199
and your cooking has improved too.

75
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,079
You and I, living together,

76
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,800
it's just perfect.

77
00:04:33,199 --> 00:04:34,639
Since when is it "perfect"?

78
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,480
With your so-called skills,

79
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,839
how can you match with me?

80
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:40,199
After all this time together,

81
00:04:40,639 --> 00:04:42,160
I feel like you're just like a man.

82
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:44,279
You're the one who's like a man!

83
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:47,079
Oh, you are a man.

84
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,839
I mean,

85
00:04:49,279 --> 00:04:50,759
you carry everything on your own.

86
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,480
Hardship or grievance,

87
00:04:52,839 --> 00:04:53,839
you keep it all inside.

88
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,519
That must be very hard on you.

89
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:01,959
Since I met you,

90
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,279
I've started

91
00:05:04,439 --> 00:05:05,920
to plan my future.

92
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:11,000
What kind of future?

93
00:05:16,519 --> 00:05:18,519
A future with hardship and difficulty,

94
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:21,000
with joy and happiness,

95
00:05:21,839 --> 00:05:22,720
but we carry

96
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:24,879
and share as one.

97
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:46,839
Your Majesty.

98
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:48,560
Jing Liuli has no clear background.

99
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,199
She appeared suddenly by your side,

100
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,680
made her way into the palace,

101
00:05:51,959 --> 00:05:53,519
and in no time at all, bewitched you

102
00:05:53,639 --> 00:05:54,560
to earn your deep favor.

103
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,480
She is a remnant spy

104
00:05:56,639 --> 00:05:58,160
of the Xiling rebels.

105
00:05:58,639 --> 00:06:00,639
Her approach to Your Majesty
is purely malicious.

106
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:01,839
I have proof.

107
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:05,079
I beg Your Majesty to see the truth.

108
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:07,000
I am loyal to Your Majesty.

109
00:06:07,639 --> 00:06:08,319
Miss Zhao,

110
00:06:08,639 --> 00:06:10,040
His Majesty has important matters today.

111
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:10,800
Please take your leave.

112
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:12,680
Your Majesty.

113
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,720
This matter concerns your life.

114
00:06:16,959 --> 00:06:17,759
I have a witness.

115
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,600
This woman is the witness.

116
00:06:23,879 --> 00:06:25,639
She knows all of Jing Liuli's secrets.

117
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,000
Who are you?

118
00:06:28,639 --> 00:06:29,639
Your Majesty,

119
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,480
I am from the music house.

120
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,000
I am here to report Consort Li.

121
00:06:33,279 --> 00:06:34,639
She is a spy from Xiling.

122
00:06:35,079 --> 00:06:37,439
Your Majesty, this woman can testify

123
00:06:37,839 --> 00:06:38,800
that Jing Liuli is

124
00:06:38,839 --> 00:06:40,639
a surviving spy from Xiling.

125
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,879
She sneaked into the palace
to seek revenge.

126
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,879
She also coerced Xiaoqing

127
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:47,040
to stay at the music house as her cover.

128
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:50,000
Every word I speak is true.

129
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,399
Everything I do is
for the good of the kingdom.

130
00:06:52,759 --> 00:06:53,759
If Your Majesty does not believe me,

131
00:06:54,079 --> 00:06:55,519
summon Jing Liuli

132
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:57,120
and confront her now.

133
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,079
Your Majesty.

134
00:07:02,639 --> 00:07:04,240
If Consort Li is truly innocent,

135
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,360
she won't shrink from a confrontation.

136
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,120
If you hesitate,

137
00:07:08,399 --> 00:07:10,199
people will talk,

138
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:12,120
and that
will only undermine your authority.

139
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,000
Summon Consort Li.

140
00:07:16,639 --> 00:07:17,120
Yes.

141
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:26,920
Jing Liuli,

142
00:07:27,439 --> 00:07:28,680
you might as well confess now.

143
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:31,160
Your approach to His Majesty
is hardly innocent.

144
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,759
You intended to assassinate His Majesty,

145
00:07:33,399 --> 00:07:35,240
and yet he treated you so well.

146
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:38,759
Your Majesty, please see it clearly.

147
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:41,480
I have been orphaned since childhood,

148
00:07:41,959 --> 00:07:43,000
wandering everywhere.

149
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:45,199
I was taken in
by the music house by chance.

150
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:47,639
I performed to make a living.

151
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:48,879
I don't know why

152
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:51,160
I've been accused of
being a spy from Xiling.

153
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:53,680
The proof and the witness are here.
How dare you deny it?

154
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,120
Xiaoqing?

155
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,000
Why are you here?

156
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,879
Why didn't you tell me you were coming?

157
00:08:09,079 --> 00:08:10,040
Your Majesty,

158
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,720
I grew up in the music house.

159
00:08:13,279 --> 00:08:14,680
But Miss Liuli

160
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:16,759
came to the music house recently.

161
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,040
She's not clear.

162
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:20,759
Jing Liuli forced the music house
to take her in,

163
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:24,839
pretended to be a court singer,
and plotted to enter the palace.

164
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:27,480
Xiaoqing,

165
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:29,839
is your gown made of Fuguang Silk?

166
00:08:30,199 --> 00:08:31,639
Yes, so what?

167
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,440
You once told me

168
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:36,720
that Fuguang Silk was your favorite.

169
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,600
But working at the music house,

170
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:41,080
we earn so little each month.

171
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:44,639
How could we afford such luxury?

172
00:08:46,399 --> 00:08:48,200
We've only been apart for a month.

173
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:51,679
Why are you suddenly so well-off?

174
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,720
It's... It's...

175
00:08:57,919 --> 00:09:00,039
It's because some generous guests

176
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,559
visited the music house recently.

177
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:09,039
We grew up together,

178
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,320
we suffered together,

179
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:13,440
and endured beatings for each other.

180
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,440
Even the leftovers nobody else wanted,

181
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,679
we would always share with each other

182
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:20,840
the moment we got them.

183
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:23,320
The bond we forged in childhood,

184
00:09:24,679 --> 00:09:26,120
did you throw it away?

185
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:32,000
Do you remember when we were eight,

186
00:09:32,759 --> 00:09:34,000
when we were being beaten

187
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:36,000
and broke the house owner's vase?

188
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:39,240
That's when you got
this crescent-shaped scar on your hand.

189
00:09:40,039 --> 00:09:42,039
And the countless scars on your hands

190
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:44,480
left behind from years of humiliation.

191
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,960
Did you throw all our memories away?

192
00:09:49,159 --> 00:09:50,320
I didn't.

193
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:51,799
Sheng.

194
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:53,600
Check her.

195
00:09:53,799 --> 00:09:54,240
Yes.

196
00:10:00,799 --> 00:10:01,279
Your Majesty,

197
00:10:01,559 --> 00:10:02,919
Consort Li's words are true.

198
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:10,000
I didn't grow up with you.
You have no clear past.

199
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:18,080
If Your Majesty does not believe me,

200
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,279
you may question the house owner

201
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:22,600
to verify my words.

202
00:10:23,559 --> 00:10:24,799
You may also check

203
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:26,799
the account books
in the west wing of the music house

204
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:29,120
to see what kind of guest

205
00:10:29,559 --> 00:10:30,399
could afford to buy her

206
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:32,360
this priceless Fuguang Silk.

207
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:35,440
All my words are true.

208
00:10:36,039 --> 00:10:37,600
Your Majesty, please see the truth.

209
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,759
Xiaoqing,

210
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:43,840
if the truth comes out,

211
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:46,639
your crime of deceiving the King
will be proven.

212
00:10:47,799 --> 00:10:49,200
According to imperial laws,

213
00:10:49,879 --> 00:10:51,279
your limbs will be severed.

214
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:54,639
Think about your family.
Who will look after them?

215
00:10:58,000 --> 00:11:00,600
Zhao Sisi was just released days ago.

216
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,799
And I am the newly titled Consort Li.

217
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,639
His Majesty is here.

218
00:11:06,559 --> 00:11:08,279
Will you be a pawn
to frame the innocent,

219
00:11:08,799 --> 00:11:11,919
or will you come clean
and save yourself?

220
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:16,039
The choice is yours.

221
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,279
Think carefully.

222
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:21,799
Please uphold justice
and reveal the truth.

223
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:27,679
Your Majesty, I am guilty.

224
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:29,799
I was bribed by Zhao Sisi.

225
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,360
She threatened me

226
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:35,960
and made me accuse Jing Liuli
of being a spy from Xiling.

227
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:38,320
I am just an ordinary woman.

228
00:11:38,759 --> 00:11:40,879
To protect myself and my family,

229
00:11:41,639 --> 00:11:42,559
I have no option but to agree.

230
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,519
I was so foolish!

231
00:11:44,799 --> 00:11:45,759
You slandered me out of thin air!

232
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:47,279
Do you have any proof?

233
00:11:50,799 --> 00:11:52,639
This is Zhao Sisi's personal belonging.

234
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,000
She gave me this as proof,

235
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,799
promising that after the job was done,

236
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,639
she would give me a lot of money

237
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,279
and ensure my safety.

238
00:11:59,919 --> 00:12:01,320
I had no choice.

239
00:12:01,519 --> 00:12:03,039
I beg Your Majesty to see clearly.

240
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,639
Your Majesty, she's lying!

241
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,320
She stole my jade pendant!

242
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:10,759
Your Majesty,

243
00:12:11,279 --> 00:12:12,679
I have never lied to you.

244
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,240
The only thing I've hidden

245
00:12:14,639 --> 00:12:15,440
is the hardship

246
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:16,519
and bitterness

247
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:19,320
while mastering my skill.

248
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,519
Your Majesty, she's lying!

249
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:22,799
Please believe me!

250
00:12:23,039 --> 00:12:24,639
She is a spy from Xiling!

251
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:25,919
Silence!

252
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,840
You keep causing trouble again and again

253
00:12:29,159 --> 00:12:30,039
with no remorse.

254
00:12:30,519 --> 00:12:31,039
Guards!

255
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:33,200
Throw her into death row.

256
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,000
Unless dead,

257
00:12:35,399 --> 00:12:36,960
she shall never see
the light of day again.

258
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,200
- Yes!
- Your Majesty!

259
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,360
Your Majesty!

260
00:12:39,559 --> 00:12:40,600
Ling Xiao!

261
00:12:40,799 --> 00:12:41,399
Your Majesty!

262
00:12:41,559 --> 00:12:42,639
She's lying!

263
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:45,519
I just love you too much,

264
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:00,840
Your Majesty!

265
00:13:02,679 --> 00:13:04,159
I'm feeling unwell

266
00:13:05,639 --> 00:13:06,679
and will take my leave now.
